# PHASES.gal

## Purpose
Defines the development and deployment phases for the Galaxy Node Pool and Node components, following the Gelato Protocol standard.

## Phase 1: Core Infrastructure (Current)
- Implement public pool registry with gRPC API
- Node registration, heartbeat, and discovery
- Basic plugin system
- Docker containerization
- Main net federation (basic)

## Phase 2: Private/Enterprise Pools
- Authentication and authorization
- Organization-specific pools
- Enhanced security features
- Advanced plugin system
- Improved main net integration with fee distribution

## Phase 3: Advanced Federation
- Cross-pool discovery
- Load balancing
- Geographic distribution
- High availability
- Advanced metrics and monitoring
- Full main net services integration

## Phase 4: Ecosystem Growth
- Third-party plugin marketplace
- Advanced orchestration
- AI-powered node selection
- Predictive scaling
- Full protocol compliance validation

